dialogue.text: Hi BF, it's meeee! Liaaaa. Remember me? It's been sooo longgg!
Okay, who the hell interrupted my damn yoga session...
Oh holy shit, haha, it's you. Nice threads, kid.
Alright, now explain to me why the hell I'm here and not shooting you in the goddamn face right now.
Nuh uh, that'll be my job, hun. Looks like killing Stephanie caused a little time rift to form. How can I not take up the offer to kill ya?
Ain't no way she just called me 'hun' like that unironically. Wait, who the hell...
I have no idea how we got here, but it ain't good.
School shooter and Don Juan, perfect.
ENOUGH! Dialogue gone on for way too long now, I just wanna kill ya for good this time. Luckily I brought my girls with me too.
You focus on her, cinnamon skin and I will blast these mfs.
Don't mind me, I'll let ya'll idiots kill each other. If a bullet touches this perfect skin, i'm tearing a rift in your assholes.
Alright, get started. I'm tryna listen to some sick tunes.
